Total energy = 3 × E₁ + 3 × E₂
Total energy = 3 × 4.423 × 10⁻²⁰ + 3 × 1.826 × 10⁻²⁰
Total energy = 1.327 × 10⁻¹⁹ + 5.478 × 10⁻²⁰
Total energy = 1.875 × 10⁻¹⁹ J

