0.17 = 0.0595 + 0.0715 + P(I ∩ L)
P(I ∩ L) = 0.17 - 0.131 = 0.039

Now I need P(R ∩ L):
Since R and I are complementary for heartbeat status:
P(R ∩ L) = P(L) - P(I ∩ L)
P(R ∩ L) = 0.19 - 0.039 = 0.151

Converting to percentage:
0.151 × 100 = 15.1%

